item.title: Kenya
item.description: Kenya, located in East Africa, is known for its diverse culture, rich traditions, and vibrant heritage. The country is home to numerous ethnic groups, each contributing to the unique cultural tapestry of Kenya. These diverse ethnicities contribute to the cultural vibrancy of the country. Kenya has a rich tradition of artistic expression. Local artisans create intricate wood carvings, beadwork, pottery, and traditional textiles. Kenya is also known for its high-quality coffee and tea production.
